modName: Self-Created Dragon Ball Super Angel's Staff
summary:
This weapon mod is based on the anime Dragon Ball Super, more accurately angel Whis of Universe 7.
In this mod, you will see several staffs of fire magic, frost magic, shock magic.

And all staffs can't be crafted, but you can use AddItemMenu to get them

This weapon mod is based on the anime Dragon Ball Super, more accurately angel Whis of Universe 7. 
In this mod, you will see several staffs of fire magic, frost magic and shock magic. 

There is no requirements for this mod. If you like it, just install it.  And all staffs can't be crafted, but you can use [b][u][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/64905]AddItemMenu[/url][/u][/b] to get them
